<br>
After all preparations are done (making Groups, Buffing, Hotbuttons (all should have an assist button)) Monk starts pulling (first u have to kill the 2 Wurms down the stairs - level 60ties if i remind right). They are hard to split cause of the room the Monk has so please all stand back and wait till main tank shout to attack) - on pulls all stand please!!! <br>
Main tank engage the mob and tank/taunt him for 10 seconds using devensive disciplines. <br>
While main tank building agro Bard should debuff the mob using Occlusion of Sounds (30 resistance debuff unresistable) - as soon done msg %T is debuffed so enchanter/magican/shaman know they can start debuffing now (Shaman/Magican with Malosi Serie and Enchanter with Tashani Serie). <br>
As soon the mob is dispelled enchanter or shaman try to slow the mob. <br>
After main tank built agro he shout Engage %T and this is the sign for all tanks to attack - plz try to attack from the max. Melee range. <br>
If disc fades or Main Tank down Main Tank 2 move forward and build agro (see M.T.T) <br>
Only Maintank use TAUNT !!!! <br>
at 50% Casters nuke the bad mofo to death :-) <br>
If you get agro DONT RUN!!! STAND AND HOPE MAIN TANK GET THE MOB OF YOU - if not wait for the rez window. Ping Pong will only get others killed!!! <br>
If you die consent all clerics with rezsticks. <br>
Loot and hope it has an armor piece <br>
